ISLAMABAD, Jan 3 (APP): Minister of State for Power Division Muhammad Hashim Notezai and Minister for Inter-Provincial Coordination Divison (IPC) Ehsan ur Rehman Mazari on Tuesday separately called on Prime Minister Muhammad Shehbaz Sharif.
During their meetings, matters related to the relevant ministries of power and IPC divisions, promotion of harmony among the provinces on different issues and the overall political situation was discussed, PM Office Media Wing said in a press release.
